project_descr: The project aims to strengthen Palestinian National Unity by addressing issues pertaining to  national reconciliation, civil service reintegration, improving local  capacities and planning schemes, as well as  the social cohesion of Palestinian society.

outputs.output_descr: The project aims at anchoring national unity and social cohesion throughout the Palestinian society through support to consolidated governance mechanisms, social reconciliation, & enhanced civic engagement.
